Package: zzrenvcheck
Title: Validate R Package Dependencies for Reproducibility
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: Validates that all R packages used in source code are properly
    declared in DESCRIPTION and locked in a 'renv' lockfile for
    reproducibility. Provides automatic detection of package usage,
    dependency validation, and auto-fix capabilities through the CRAN API.
